quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  23,23,"“Ndipo ndithu tidamtuma Nuh kwa anthu ake, ndipo adati: “E inu anthu anga! Mpembedzeni Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina woti nkumpembedza kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa (chilango Chake)"
  23,24,"“Akuluakulu mwa anthu ake amene sadakhulupirire, adati: “Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu ngati inu; akufuna kuti adzipezere ubwino pa inu; ndipo Allah akadafuna (kukuphunzitsani) akadatuma angelo. Zoterezi sitidamvepo kumakolo athu akale.”"
  23,25,"““Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu wamisala; choncho muyembekezereni mpaka nthawi (yofera.”)"
  23,26,"“(Nuh) adati: “Mbuye wanga ndipulumutseni pazomwe anditsutsa!”"
  23,27,"“Choncho tidamuvumbulutsira (mawu akuti): “Panga chombo moyang’aniridwa ndi kudziwitsidwa ndi Ife.” Ndipo lamulo Lathu likadza ndi kufwamphuka madzi mu uvuni, lowetsa mkati mwake (mwa chombocho) chilichonse ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi ndi banja lako, kupatula yemwe liwu latsogola pa iye kuti aonongeke mwa iwo. Ndipo usandilankhule za omwe adzichitira (okha) zoipa ndithu iwo amizidwa (m’madzi)"
  23,28,"“Ndipo ukakhazikika m’chombocho, iwe ndi amene uli nawo, nena: “Tikuthokoza Allah, amene watipulumutsa ku anthu osalungama.”"
  23,29,"“Ndipo (potsika), nena: “E Mbuye wanga! Nditsitseni; kutsitsa kwa madalitso, pakuti Inu ndinu wotsitsa bwino kwambiri kuposa otsitsa.”"
  23,30,“Ndithu m’zimenezi muli zisonyezo. Ndithu Ife tili (ndi udindo) wowayesa ndi mayeso osiyanasiyana
  23,31,“Kenako tidabweretsa m’badwo wina pambuyo pawo (omwe ndi Âdi)
  23,32,"“Ndipo tidatuma kwa iwo mtumiki (Hûd) wochokera mwa iwo, (yemwe ankati): “Pembedzani Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa"